<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1033289096">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}</style><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Harry Patterson" redirects here. For the American printer and botanist, see <a href="/wiki/Harry_Norton_Patterson" title="Harry Norton Patterson">Harry Norton Patterson</a>. For the president of Maryland Agricultural College, see <a href="/wiki/Harry_J._Patterson" title="Harry J. Patterson">Harry J. Patterson</a>.</div>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1033289096"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">For other people named Jack Higgins, see <a href="/wiki/Jack_Higgins_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Jack Higgins (disambiguation)">Jack Higgins (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
